# PED::GET_HEAD_BLEND_EYE_COLOR

## Summary
Gets the specified eye color index on the given ped

## Parameters
* **PED_INDEX** ped

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
A getter for _SET_PED_EYE_COLOR. Returns -1 if fails to get.
